Package soot.jimple.infoflow.android.axml

Class AXmlHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.jimple.infoflow.android.axml.AXmlHandler
  • public class AXmlHandler
extends Object
    AXmlHandler provides functionality to parse a byte compressed android xml file and access all nodes.
    Author:
    Stefan Haas, Mario Schlipf
